Package cams.dashboards.menu

Class CommitteeUI

java.lang.Object
cams.dashboards.menu.UserUI
cams.dashboards.menu.StudentUI
cams.dashboards.menu.CommitteeUI
All Implemented Interfaces:
DashboardState
public class CommitteeUI
extends StudentUI
Represents the dashboard state for a committee member. This class extends StudentUI and adds additional functionalities specific to committee members, such as managing suggestions, replying to enquiries, and generating reports.
